OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with clear spells at first
OL,7,Fbut soon turning cloudier. Remaining
OL,8,Fcloudy overnight with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain spreading northwards. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning.
OL,13,FMostly dry in the afternoon with some
OL,14,Fbrightness in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
